				<div class="fourteen columns offset-by-one alpha">
					<div class="typography"><p>Since 1932, Curt G. Joa, Inc. has been known for innovation in the disposable hygiene industry. Our team of engineers, technicians and assembly staff work together with customers to create custom, inventive and efficient converting machines that have made Joa the standard in quality equipment worldwide.</p></div>
