		<div class="home-stats double-top double-bottom clearfix">
			<div class="a"><p>Since</p><h2>1932</h2><p class="lower">Joa has been a leader in the industry</p></div>
			<div class="b"><p>Joa machines operate in</p><h2>55</h2><p class="lower">countries across the world</p></div>
			<div class="c"><p>Modern plant occupies over</p><h2>35K</h2><p class="lower">sq. meters</p></div>
			<div class="d"><p>Joa has over</p><h2>7600</h2><p class="lower">sq. meters of secure testing space</p></div>
