						<h4>New Joa European Technology Team</h4>
						
							<p>Located in Mayen, Germany, the Joa European Technology Team
serves customers in the European Region. The Joa European
Technology Team supports both JOA and BIKOMA machines and
future projects from its Mayen location for the European
market.</p>
						
